  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you use the <strong>Attack </strong>action on your turn, you can spend 1 @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.imsZ2GYUPlwCQqqy]{ki point} to cause tendrils of flame to stretch out from your fists and feet. Your reach with your unarmed strikes increases by <strong>10 feet</strong> for that action, as well as the rest of the turn. A hit with such an attack deals fire damage instead of bludgeoning damage, and if you spend 1 ki point when the attack hits, it also deals an extra 1d10 fire damage.</p>\n<section class=\"secret\">\n<p><em>Note: After adding this feature to your character, set Resource Consumption to Item Uses: Ki.</em></p>\n<p><em>Use this feature once to \"activate\" the ability. From then on, alt-click this feature to deal the appropriate fire damage.</em></p>\n</section>",
